      <procstep>
        <procdesc>Dataset copied from the cd obtained from Washington, DC 2005

Data from the Digital Aeronautical Flight Information File (DAFIF) was downloaded locally.  All files were brought into ArcMap and re projected to DC Standard Maryland State Plane NAD83.  The two features were represented in separate shapefiles.  They were merged into one shapefile and all relevant attribute data was maintained.</procdesc>
        <procdate>2006</procdate>
